    <p>DAVID WELNA: It was only five months ago that Christopher Dodd summoned reporters to his Connecticut home to say he was being treated for prostate cancer and seeking a sixth term in the Senate. </p>
    <p>Senator CHRISTOPHER DODD (Democrat, Connecticut): I'm running the reelection. </p>
