    <p>RAZ: So as your coin is spinning through the air, I can watch a computer version in real time flipping on the JumboTron. </p>
    <p>LARCHUK: Exactly. And you can even see which side the coin lands on before the ref does. </p>
    <p>RAZ: This is ridiculous. Why would anybody ever invent this? </p>
    <p>LARCHUK: Well, it's the age-old story, Guy. If you can get everyone in the stadium's eyes glued up there on the JumboTron during the coin toss, you could put an ad up there and make some money. </p>
    <p>RAZ: Of course. That's one of our producers, Travis Larchuk. Travis, thanks. </p>
    <p>LARCHUK: No problem, Guy. </p>
