    <p>Mr.�DAISEY: All money is power. All power corrupts. But we can't go through life  most of us can't, I know I can't - go through life totally divorced from money. I need money. In fact, I love money. At the same time, I have to recognize that the more money I have, the more it corrupts. </p>
