    <p>Ms. PETERKIN: I hope to. </p>
    <p>ROSE: But you're not sure. </p>
    <p>Ms. PETERKIN: Yeah. </p>
    <p>ROSE: Teroi Peterkin is eating lunch at The Hub with some friends. They all voted for Obama, and while they haven't given up on him yet, you can definitely sense a little impatience. Here's Kalid Brandon Hatcher(ph). </p>
