    <p>JAFFE: None of this means she isn't still thrilled that an African-American is now president of the United States. For Cordon Porter, that rises above any disappointments. </p>
    <p>Mr. PORTER: One thing that I can always say, just like I told you, we can be anything we want to be. And that means a lot to me. </p>
